grammarModel.genericTools

Interface IPosetMaxChains

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IChains
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PosetMaxChains

    public interface IPosetMaxChains
extends IChains
    PosetMaxChains represents the spanning chains of a lower semilattice. It provides navigation functionalities and an access to the set of implications associated with the semilattice.
    Author:
    Gael Tregouet
